{"tid":1537034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家明白前線記者有自己既職責","createTime":"2019-09-03T19:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T19:15:59.000Z","uid":135274,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a97c07eaf7cccedb8bad8f94fec2fa7409c5ad1e","tid":1537034,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:10:21.000Z","msg":"1. 黑警一定有控制中心，可以睇全部傳媒既live<br />\n2. 就算記者冇影到架42C，都會有車上既藍絲篤灰<br />\n<br />\n記者著得起反光背心，就有自己既職責。特別對於直播黎講，佢係有必要用一個盡量中立既角度去拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n有啲時候，記者喺角度上有走棧既地方；但就算真係拍到，都屬於佢地既職責之內，嚴格上黎講係冇錯。<br />\n<br />\n點解記者可以拍到咁多黑警濫暴既情況？係因為黑警本身質素低。但直播鏡頭係一個雙面刃，手足既行為都一定會拍到。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我希望前線手足可以提高自己安全意識，準備好逃生路線，唔好係鏡頭前換衫、dum gear。"},{"pid":"b8ca3ff7521fb1d90709c183a4debad9a3670a8f","tid":1537034,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d533c2abe2b4effb3e8ebacce0a33c5d6e6bc2df","tid":1537034,"uid":97330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:10:56.000Z","msg":"閃電勇武係唔洗代價架！<br />\n而且少人就成事，大家諗下一個廢老咁慢手腳都可以清晒連儂牆<br />\n對家打埋啲陰陰濕濕既招，我地都可以陰陰濕濕快閃一啲有價值既地方<br />\n十八區都有既時候 啲狗跑得去邊？ 2個人一個地方 36個人都夠<br />\n<br />\n重點：非狗屋 五分鐘快閃 (五分鐘就走邊有人當場拉到? 快閃既定義本身就係咁)"},{"pid":"caa85ab67a73c6049ea7feaf396a86176fe94905","tid":1537034,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:11:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2813bee63fa4d76977cc63a8a801164fe5d9d64b","tid":1537034,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:12:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3be22a85c4a75538c84dd7ff1f8982d44537f102","tid":1537034,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"334e01c474f3ae27282395963bef13473caa8490","tid":1537034,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:15:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iBWrQR5.jpg\" data-thumbna